## Citation Information

### Preferred Citation (BibTeX)

```bibtex
@article{ranjan2025unpaid,
  title={Economic Valuation of Unpaid Labor in Indian Marriages: Complete Mathematical Framework and Transparency Volume},
  author={Ranjan, Ashish},
  journal={Independent Research Series},
  year={2025},
  month={September},
  doi={[DOI will be assigned upon publication]},
  url={https://github.com/ashishrjsingh/unpaid-labor-valuation},
  note={Replication package available at: https://github.com/ashishrjsingh/unpaid-labor-valuation}
}
```

### Preferred Citation (APA Style)

Ranjan, A. (2025). Economic valuation of unpaid labor in Indian marriages: Complete mathematical framework and transparency volume. *Independent Research Series*. https://github.com/ashishrjsingh/unpaid-labor-valuation

### Preferred Citation (Chicago Style)

Ranjan, Ashish. "Economic Valuation of Unpaid Labor in Indian Marriages: Complete Mathematical Framework and Transparency Volume." *Independent Research Series* (2025). https://github.com/ashishrjsingh/unpaid-labor-valuation.

### Replication Package Citation

If citing the replication package specifically:

```bibtex
@misc{ranjan2025replication,
  title={Replication Package for "Economic Valuation of Unpaid Labor in Indian Marriages"},
  author={Ranjan, Ashish},
  year={2025},
  month={September},
  howpublished={GitHub repository},
  url={https://github.com/ashishrjsingh/unpaid-labor-valuation},
  version={1.0},
  note={Computational replication materials following AEA guidelines}
}
```

### Data Sources Citations

When using this replication package, please also cite the primary data sources:

**India Time Use Survey 2019:**
```bibtex
@techreport{mospi2019tus,
  title={Time Use in India - 2019},
  author={{Ministry of Statistics and Programme Implementation}},
  institution={Government of India},
  year={2019},
  url={http://mospi.nic.in/time-use-survey}
}
```

**Labour Bureau Minimum Wages:**
```bibtex
@misc{labour2025wages,
  title={Minimum Wages Database},
  author={{Labour Bureau}},
  institution={Government of India},
  year={2025},
  url={https://labour.gov.in/minimum-wages}
}
```

